{"tid":1394794,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒癮22年] 中國停辦香港遊等於開始戒毒","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:38:51.000Z","uid":41458,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95322e2e8f6001dcdc9c367899b9f56ce69fc87a","tid":1394794,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港反修《逃犯條例》風波持續，有內地居民感覺香港情況混亂，不到香港旅遊，有內地旅行社更停辦所有香港遊。 <br />\n<br />\n正值旅遊旺季，但廣州居民這個暑假都不來香港，有旅行社表示，自上星期起少了很多旅客查詢到香港旅遊的資訊，有一間旅行社看不見香港遊的宣傳，職員指收到通知，已停辦所有香港團。不過旅行社指，香港仍是內地居民外遊的熱門地點，相信風波過後，到香港旅遊的人數會回升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/553860/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%85%E7%A4%BE%E5%81%9C%E8%BE%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F553860%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%258A&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=c6b26a5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F553860%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%258A&h=5b156b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/553860/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%97%85%E7%A4%BE%E5%81%9C%E8%BE%A6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8A</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-